        "quote_color": "#2b2fd9",
        "eyebrow_text": "THE GAP",
        "body_text": "You've tried the hyaluronic acids, the vitamin C serums, the retinol night creams. Your shelf is full of half-used bottles that promised radiance and delivered... fine.",
        "pull_quote": "What if the most potent ingredients for your skin have never been seen in Western skincare — sourced from the rarest corners of India, bio-engineered in New York City, and precision-formulated for clinical results?",
