    "mmx_reasons": {
      "type": "mmx-reasons",
      "blocks": {
        "reason_1": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "#f8f3ee",
            "image_position": "auto",
            "mobile_stack_order": "image_first",
            "icon": "eye",
            "headline": "It Contains an Ingredient So Rare, Surgeons Use It",
            "body": "<p>Most serums hydrate. This one performs. The Dewdrops contain Liquefied Gold Muga Silk — a rarefied regenerative material used in surgical wound repair, sourced exclusively from Assam, India. It drives skin cell regeneration at a cellular level. A precision-grade, bio-tech ingredient that luxury labs are only beginning to unlock.</p>",
            "testimonial_quote": "Shocked at the difference in just a few days. My skin absorbs it instantly — super soft and glowy.",
            "testimonial_author": "Julie O., Verified Buyer",
            "cta_text": "TRY THE SURGICAL-GRADE SERUM",
            "cta_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Raw_Muga_Copper-Crusted_Silk_Cocoons.png",
            "image_alt": ""
          }
        },
        "reason_2": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "#ffffff",
            "image_position": "auto",
            "mobile_stack_order": "image_first",
            "icon": "moon",
            "headline": "The Tea Inside Was Harvested Under a Full Moon",
            "body": "<p>Silver Tips Imperial Tea from Darjeeling's Makaibari Estate. Plucked only on clear, full-moon nights at peak potency — one of the most expensive, undiscovered teas in the world.</p><p>Dense in polyphenols and bio-active compounds, it shields skin fromenvironmental aggressors while delivering a glass-like, luminous complexion.Love, Indus is the only skincare brand using this ingredient.</p>",
            "testimonial_quote": "My skin has never looked this radiant. I can actually see the difference every morning.",
            "testimonial_author": "Sarah K., Verified Buyer",
            "cta_text": "EXPERIENCE FULL-MOON RADIANCE",
            "cta_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Silver_Tips_Imperial_Tea_leaves.png",
            "image_alt": ""
          }
        },
        "reason_3": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "",
            "image_position": "auto",
            "mobile_stack_order": "image_first",
            "icon": "drop",
            "headline": "It Replaced Five Steps in My Routine",
            "body": "<p>Hydrator. Illuminator. Barrier serum. Firming Complex. Precision exfoliation. Five high-performance steps — one cutting-edge formula.</p><p>Dermatologists are moving toward fewer, more potent products. Four SilkCocoons included free. Each lasts up to 4 uses — one set carries you 3–4 months.</p>",
            "testimonial_quote": "My routine is completely transformed. The Silk Cocoons are unlike anything I've seen in high-performance skincare.",
            "testimonial_author": "Rachael M., Verified Buyer",
            "cta_text": "SIMPLIFY TO ONE BOTTLE",
            "cta_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Minimalist_vanity_with_single_serum.png",
            "image_alt": ""
          }
        },
        "reason_4": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "#ffffff",
            "image_position": "auto",
            "mobile_stack_order": "image_first",
            "icon": "award",
            "headline": "Vogue Called It a Best Spring Product for a Reason",
            "body": "<p>Vogue's \"Best Spring Product\" evaluates innovation and ingredient integrity. TheDewdrops combine clinical-grade Niacinamide + Sodium Hyaluronate withrarefied regional ingredients never seen in Western skincare.</p><p>Emmy-winning makeup artist Alexandra French (Euphoria S2) uses them. Whenthe artists behind the beauty looks you admire choose this product, that saysmore than any ad.</p>",
            "testimonial_quote": "I've tried every luxury serum on the market. Nothing compares to this.",
            "testimonial_author": "Priya D., Verified Buyer",
            "cta_text": "AWARD-WINNING FORMULA",
            "cta_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Vogue_and_press_clippings.png",
            "image_alt": ""
          }
        },
        "reason_5": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "",
            "image_position": "auto",
            "mobile_stack_order": "image_first",
            "icon": "leaf",
            "headline": "Rare Regional Ingredients Your Dermatologist Has Never Heard Of",
            "body": "<p>Liquefied Gold Muga Silk — the absolute hero — drives skin cell renewal at a cellular level. Ashwagandha Root Extract neutralizes cortisol-driven skin damage. Tremella Mushroom — a rare cloud fungus — holds 500x its weight in moisture. </p><p>The formula also includes Copper for antimicrobial and skin-strengthening benefits, Niacinamide for visible brightening, and Hyaluronic Acid for deep, lasting hydration. Finished with Tuberose — rare, aromatic, and deeply restorative.</p><p>Undiscovered by Western skincare. Precision-validated by NYC bio-tech formulation science. All, in one dropper.</p>",
            "testimonial_quote": "The ingredient list reads like a scientific breakthrough. My skin has never looked this luminous or glass-like.",
            "testimonial_author": "Amara J., Verified Buyer",
            "cta_text": "DISCOVER THE RARE INGREDIENTS",
            "cta_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Rare_regional_Indian_ingredients_Ashwagandha_Tremella_Hibiscus.png",
            "image_alt": ""
          }
        },
        "reason_6": {
          "type": "reason",
          "settings": {
            "background_color": "#ffffff",
            "image_position": "auto",
            "mobile_stack_order": "image_first",
            "icon": "drop",
            "headline": "It Sold Out in 11 Minutes. Then 400 People Joined the Waitlist.",
            "body": "<p>1,250 units on QVC. Gone in 11 minutes. 400+ on the waitlist — not because of acampaign, because the clinical results speak for themselves.</p><p>After four weeks: tighter, firmer, dewy, visibly more luminous skin. Fine linesrecede. The Dewdrops are back in stock — but they won't last.</p>",
            "testimonial_quote": "After 4 weeks, my skin is super smooth with a lovely glow. Fine lines less visible. Tighter, firmer, most luminous.",
            "testimonial_author": "Betty B., Verified Buyer",
            "cta_text": "CLAIM YOUR BOTTLE",
            "cta_url": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Close-up_luminous_radiant_skin.png",
            "image_alt": ""
          }
        }
      },
